				"string" : "{{ txt .}}\n1 - first player at or below zero hit points loses\n2 - damage taken each turn is either amount OR one damage whichever is greater.\n3 - On each of your turns, you must select one of your spells to cast. If you cannot afford to cast any spell, you lose.\n4 - Effects apply at the start of both the player's turns and the boss' turns.\n\nAOC2015Day22Game object \nplayer starts with ?? hit points and ?? armor and ?? mana and several effects \nboss has N hit points and pretty much nothing else\n\nGame >> Reset \n player to move\n\nGAME >> TURN\n \n PLAYERS TURN\n  apply all spells and reduce their count by 1 to min of zero (max 0 effectCount)\n   if  PLAYER hit points <= 0 then BOSS has won\n  choose a spell to cast - only spell with spell count  of zero can be cast , \n  one spell must be chosen , if cannot afford any spell , player loses \n-- call TURN\n \n BOSS TURN\n  apply all spells and reduce their count by 1 to min of zero (max 0 effectCount)\n if boss hit points <= 0 then player has won\n boss deals 8 damage\n -- call TURN\n \nSTART: \nplayer must choose a spell to cast \neffect counter set to initial value and \n\nBOSS :\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"
			},
