				"code" : "\"Magic Missile costs 53 mana. It instantly does 4 damage.\nDrain costs 73 mana. It instantly does 2 damage and heals you for 2 hit points.\nShield costs 113 mana. It starts an effect that lasts for 6 turns. While it is active, your armor is increased by 7.\nPoison costs 173 mana. It starts an effect that lasts for 6 turns. At the start of each turn while it is active, it deals the boss 3 damage.\nRecharge costs 229 mana. It starts an effect that lasts for 5 turns. At the start of each turn while it is active, it gives you 101 new mana.\ronly spells with active \r\rread only most properties or functional approach copy effect and then reduce active count until zero\r\"\reffects := { \r{'Magic Missile' . 1 turn . 53 mana . 4 damage . 0 heal . 0 armor . 0 mana. 0 active.} . \r{'Drain' . 1 turn . 73 mana . 2 damage . 2 heal  . 0 armor . 0 mana. 0 active.} . \r{'Shield' . 6 turn . 113 mana . 0 damage . 0 heal . 7 armor . 0 mana. 0 active.} . \r{'Poison' . 6 turn . 173 mana . 3 damage . 0 heal . 0 armor . 0 mana. 0 active .} . \r{'Recharge' . 5 turn . 229 mana . 0 damage . 0 heal . 0 armor . 101 mana. 0 active.} }."
